Sniper/Rhinox/Proto/Grimmler


Sniper sees The ship leave, and he has the felling Hell Beast was on 
it. "Damn." Sniper pulls out a rocket launcher and fires 2 Rockets at 
the Predacons Ship. He fired 4 Optic Blast at The Predacon ship.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rhinox was on Premiter Patrol. He was walking around the Premiter. He 
open a com to the Maximal base. "Sector Clear." 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Proto was on the Scanners and GRimmler weas on the com unit. Grimmler 
heard "Sector clear." Grimmler knew the voice was Rhinox. "Okay 
Rhinox, please go to Sector 20."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rhinox answered Grimmler, "I'm heading there."
